\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Highest realistic accuracy
\f0\b0 : push toward 
\f1\b 97\'9698% on mother-brand presence detection
\f0\b0  and 
\f1\b very high reviewed operational accuracy
\f0\b0 , with SKU-level exact-match accuracy improving in phases through active learning and review feedback. This target is realistic only if uncertainty is handled correctly and low-confidence cases are reviewed rather than blindly auto-approved. ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://arxiv.org/abs/1810.01733"}}{\fldrslt \cf4 \ul \ulc4 \strokec4 arXiv}})\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 2. Target outcomes\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The system will ingest one or more retail shelf images per outlet and return:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 mother brands present\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 SKUs present\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 estimated visible pack counts by brand/SKU\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 unknown / unresolved packs\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 confidence scores\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 review status\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 audit trail and model versions used\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0
\cf0 The system must explicitly distinguish between:\
