\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Why not direct SKU detection\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 The first production detector should 
\f1\b not
\f0\b0  be a flat SKU detector. A class-agnostic or coarse detector is more robust and cheaper to annotate. Exact SKU discrimination should happen later on crops.\
